                value:
                  "Incorporating the manifesto into the message requires the candidate to stress how the voter's values and policies coincide with those of the candidate and how the candidate would fight to better the lives of the voters if they are elected. Candidates should highlight their experience and qualifications for the post and their plans to address voters' top concerns in their messages.",
