                  'One of the key benefits of leveraging online platforms and digital tools is the ability to reach a larger audience. With traditional fundraising methods, such as direct mail or in-person events, there is a limit to the number of people you can get. However, online platforms allow you to quickly and easily share your campaign with many people, including those outside your immediate geographic area.',
