                  'In addition to traditional social media platforms, newer platforms like TikTok and Clubhouse can also be effective tools for fundraising. TikTok, for example, has a massive user base that skews younger and is more likely to engage in social issues. On the other hand, Clubhouse is an audio-only platform ideal for hosting virtual events and discussions.',
