                  "4. Get involved in community outreach. Community outreach is an essential component of any political campaign. In fact, it's how I and many others became involved in local politics. Start by identifying local community or interest groups, business associations, labor organizations, and activists who are engaged in issues that concern your constituents and the community at large. ",
