                value:
                  'Keep in mind that your efforts to raise funds for your campaign should be a little more subtle than "Please send me money now, even if it\'s only a few cents". Efforts toward responsive politics aside, voters are leery of politicians. That means you must carefully build relationships with donors through trust, transparency, and authenticity. ',
