                value:
                  'Good Party is not a political party instead, we are a tech company that helps good independent and 3rd party candidates run for office. Our platform provides expert knowledge and campaign tools for candidates like you looking to gain an advantage against your competitors. We provide this information for free and it can help you run more effective social media campaigns. If you’re considering a run for office, or have already completed the paperwork, you can book time with our team to learn more. ',
