                data: {},
                marks: [],
                value:
                  '\nTwo of the target user groups made up slightly more than 50% of the total responses - Jaded Jack and Dutiful Doug. This proportion indicates that the sentiment of voting for the lesser of two evils and a prevailing feeling of not knowing how to make an impact dominate the minds of independent voters.',
                nodeType: 'text',
