                data: {},
                marks: [],
                value:
                  "If you're passionate about politics and want to see change in Durham, we encourage you to run for office. We know it can be intimidating at first, but with our help, there are many ways that you can get started today. If you have any questions or would like more information about how Good Party can help your campaign, please ",
